A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Sports Venues – Reusable Beverage Containers – Use During Sporting Events
3 FOR the purpose of requiring the owner or operator of a sports venue and the governing
4 body of an institution of higher education that operates a sports venue to allow an
5 individual attending a sporting event at the sports venue to bring and use a reusable
6 beverage container during a sporting event; and generally relating to reusable
7 beverage containers and sports venues.
